xreader (1.0.1) sarah; urgency=medium

  * Fixed missing file
  * Packaging: Removed breaks/replaces
  * Compile xreader in GTK3 but the Caja extension in GTK2
  * Added nemo properties page extension
  * Use generic names in window title and menu, and update about dialog.
  * Updated figure in help, removed a few MATE references
  * Updated help
  * Removed support for MATE lockdown (DE-specific)
  * Use the presence API to inhibit the screensaver in presentation mode
  * Remove support for media-keys (requires DE-specific settings daemon)
  * Fixed Uninhiting session when leaving presentation mode (was broken by migration to presence API)
  * ev-page-action-widget: Use an insensitive entry for pages label
  * page-action-widget: Only show page number in pages label when it's different
  * Removed separators in default toolbar
  * Added makepot and pot file

 -- Clement Lefebvre <root@linuxmint.com>  Tue, 09 Feb 2016 16:12:30 +0000

